metadata.name: DIM SUM PARTY
metadata.description:
This NFT commemorates the official event collaboration between FWB, Uniswap, and Boys Club for NFT NYC 2023.

On April 11, 2023, these three communities convened over infinite dim sum, BBQ pork buns and dumplings at the famed Golden Unicorn in Chinatown. 

This Open Edition acts as an artifact of the cultural map inside the FWB ecosystem.
